reviewText:
This DVD from Azul Music is an invitation to contemplation of the beauty, peace and tranquillity of the sea with images of the rich fauna and flora of the Atlantic Ocean and Brazilian coast, including exclusive images by Project TAMAR. Musical soundtrack features the music of renowned Brazilian artists Ulisses Rocha, Marcelo Gallo and Corciolli. Dolby Digital 2.0, Dolby Digital 5.1
